  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed two storey side extension, with particular reference to its proximity to and forward projection past the neighbouring property at 127 Malvern Avenue, creates an unacceptable sense of enclosure and impacts the outlook of neighbouring windows at this property. This is considered contrary to the Policy DM1 of Harrow’s Development Management Policies Local Plan document (2013) and Harrow’s Residential Design Guide SPD (2010)&lt;/p&gt;",
    "The depth, height and siting of the proposed first floor element of the rear extension would create an unacceptable sense of enclosure and impact the outlook of the neighbouring first floor windows at both 127 and 131 Malvern Avenue. It would be contrary to the 45 degree code contained within the adopted Harrow Supplementary Planning Document Residential Design Guide (2010) and Policy DM1 of Harrow’s Development Management Policies Local Plan document (2013)."
